来，能活多久？即使现在能活着，以后的人生还有多少困难，多少病痛会一直折磨这孩子和家人？倾家荡产花出去的天价医疗费有什么能力偿还？孩子的爸爸犹豫了，到底该何去何从？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-1266ba25e04e99790afdfffc2b3b1967_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "348 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/57895213"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgrTCjquKueUUEAMaCDE1Mzc5MTA1IPCY/MYFMPwBOKlIQAtyCDU3ODk1MjEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1631077552.6713011", "card_id": "Q_478233531", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 139}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "都是刘和平编剧，为什么《雍正王朝》当年收视爆火而《大明王朝 1566》却遇冷直到十年后才小范围火起来？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-766cd3e9936d198505ee843ad8a49113_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "320 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/478233531"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgrTCjquKueUUEAMaCDY4NTU1MTQzIL/tvogGMBQ4rgRADHIJNDc4MjMzNTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1631077552.6716774", "card_id": "Q_485374020", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 172}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "黄西退出《脱口秀大会》第四季，可能有哪些原因？如何评价他的脱口秀水平？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-dbd171425308695042422b1ba02cbfb0_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "302 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/485374020"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgrTCjquKueUUEAMaCDcwMTQyODM0IL603YkGMBM4mANADXIJNDg1Mzc0MDIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1631077552.6720648", "card_id": "Q_485418486", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 144}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "12 强赛两连败之后，国足冲击 